      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/node/3516" title="Spring Web Flow 2.3.1 released">Spring Web Flow 2.3.1 released</a>
    </h2>
  
  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
          Submitted by Rossen Stoyanchev on Tue, 2012-03-27 16:48        </div>
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"> in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_4 first last"><a href="/taxonomy/term/4" rel="tag" title="News and announcements
">News and Announcements</a></li>
</ul></div>
          </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Spring Web Flow 2.3.1 is now available for <a href="http://www.springsource.com/download/community?project=Spring%20Web%20Flow">download</a>. This maintenance release includes an upgrade to Spring 3.1.1, JavaServer Faces 2.1.7 along with a number of bug fixes. For those tracking the project it is now <a href="https://github.com/SpringSource/spring-webflow">hosted on Github</a> including a separate <a href="https://github.com/SpringSource/spring-webflow-issues#readme">issue repository</a> to help reproduce issues based on one of several project templates.</p>
