<div id="node-3511" class="node node-type-story node-promoted node-teaser build-mode-teaser"><div class="node-inner">

  
      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/node/3511" title="Spring GemFire 1.1.1 Released for Java ">Spring GemFire 1.1.1 Released for Java </a>
    </h2>
  
  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
          Submitted by Costin Leau on Tue, 2012-03-20 13:27        </div>
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"> in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_4 first last"><a href="/taxonomy/term/4" rel="tag" title="News and announcements
">News and Announcements</a></li>
</ul></div>
          </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear Spring Community,</p>
<p>I am pleased to announce the GA release of Spring GemFire 1.1.1 project is now available!</p>
<p><a href="http://www.springsource.com/download/community?project=Spring GemFire&amp;version=1.1.1.RELEASE">Downloads</a> | <a href="http://static.springsource.org/spring-gemfire/docs/1.1.1.RELEASE/api/">JavaDocs</a> | <a href="http://static.springsource.org/spring-gemfire/docs/1.1.1.RELEASE/reference/">Reference Documentation</a> | <a href="http://static.springframework.org/spring-gemfire/docs/1.1.1.RELEASE/changelog.txt">Changelog</a></p>
  </div>

  <ul class="links inline"><li class="comment_forbidden first"></li>
<li class="node_read_more last"><a href="/node/3511" title="Read the rest of Spring GemFire 1.1.1 Released for Java .">Read more</a></li>
</ul>
</div></div> <!-- /node-inner, /node -->
